quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  7,179,"Mu by’ukuri, twaremeye umuriro wa Jahanamu abenshi mu majini n’abantu; bafite imitima ariko ntibatekereza, bafite amaso ariko ntibabona, banafite amatwi ariko ntibumva. Abo bameze nk’inyamaswa, ahubwo barayobye cyane. Abo ni bo barindagiye"
  7,180,"Kandiamazina meza yose ni aya Allah, bityo mujye muyifashisha mumusaba, kandi munitandukanye na babandi bakerensa amazina ye 55 . Bazahanirwa ibyo bakoraga"
  7,181,"No mu bo twaremye, harimo itsinda riyobora (abandi) rikoresheje ukuri, rikanagukoresha mu butabera"
  7,182,"Na babandi bahinyuye amagambo yacu, tuzabajyana buhoro buhoro tubahane mu buryo batazi"
  7,183,"Nzanabaha igihe (bibwire ko batazahanwa); mu by’ukuri, imigambi yanjye irakomeye"
  7,184,"Ese ntibatekereza? Mugenzi wabo (Muhamadi) si umusazi, ahubwo ni umuburizi ugaragara"
  7,185,"Ese ntibitegereza ubwami bw’ibirere n’isi, n’ibyo Allah yaremye, ndetse n’uko bishoboka ko iherezo ry’ubuzima bwabo ryegereje? Nonese ni ayahe magambo (y’ububurizi) nyuma y’aya (Qur’an) bakwemera"
  7,186,Uwo Allah yarekeye mu buyobe (kubera gukurikira irari ry’umutima we) ntawamuyobora; anabarekera mu buhakanyi bwabo barindagira
  7,187,"Barakubaza (yewe Muhamadi) kubyerekeye igihe imperuka izabera. Vuga uti \"Mu by’ukuri, ubumenyi bwayo bwihariwe na Nyagasani wanjye. Nta wundi wagaragaza igihe cyayo uretse we. Ibyayo biraremereye mu birere no ku isi. Ntizabageraho itabatunguye. Barakubaza nk’aho uyifiteho ubumenyi. Vuga uti \"Mu by’ukuri, ubumenyi bwayo bwihariwe na Allah, nyamara abenshi mu bantu ntibabizi"